      <title>Rotten Tomatoes Predictor</title>
      <statement>
        <p>Repeat the analysis for the movie data using the Rotten Tomato scores (rt_score) to predict world-wide revenue. Summarize how the results compare.</p>
      </statement>
      <response/>
